# Maestro screenshot artifacts. `takeScreenshot: <name>` writes <name>.png to
# the app root (the CWD maestro runs from), so ignore root-level PNGs too —
# legitimate image assets live under assets/ / ios/ / android/, not here.
*.screenshot.png
/*.png

